# Implementation Plan — Differentiate Owner vs Staff Access (RBAC)

This plan implements Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) to secure sensitive store financials, cost prices, profit metrics, full billing/purchase logs, and settings from Staff accounts while preserving full operational abilities for POS billing.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Test Suite Fixes
Fix pre-existing test failures in the purchases test suite caused by a recent migration that made `reference_number` (Reference Invoice Bill #) a required field, but did not update the test inputs.

#### [MODIFY] [purchases.test.ts](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/backend/tests/purchases.test.ts)
- Add `reference_number: 'REF-TEST-100'` to the mock purchase payload in the transactional tests.

