### 3. Frontend Component Guards & Premium UI Signaling
Secure the frontend layouts to ensure an intuitive, transparent experience. We use honest UI signaling (`🔒 Owner only`) rather than silently hiding critical dashboard blocks, keeping settings and analytics navigation strictly owner-only.

#### [MODIFY] [StatCard.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/shared/ui/StatCard.tsx)
- Support a `locked` boolean property.
- When `locked` is true, render a beautiful lock symbol (`🔒`) and a text label reading `"Owner only"` instead of displaying the actual statistic value and trend indicators. Disables click interactions when locked.

#### [MODIFY] [StatCard.module.css](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/shared/ui/StatCard.module.css)
- Add styles for `.lockedCard` (dashed border style, slight opacity/dimmed background using `--color-surface-dim`) and `.lockedContainer` to align with the Ice Latte + Mint design system.

#### [MODIFY] [DashboardPage.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/features/dashboard/DashboardPage.tsx)
- Pass `locked={!isOwner}` to the **Inventory Value** card, fetching the role from `useAuthStore`.

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/shared/layout/Sidebar.tsx)
- Check `user?.role` from `useAuthStore`.
- Conditionally render the **Analytics** and **Purchases** navigation links only if the user is the owner (`isOwner`).

#### [MODIFY] [ProductForm.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/features/inventory/ProductForm.tsx)
- Check user role. If the user is not an owner, hide the **Cost Price** input field entirely from the layout.
- In the submit callback, if the Cost Price is hidden (Staff mode), fallback by assigning `cost_price` to the Selling Price value to pass schema validation.

#### [MODIFY] [InventoryPage.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/features/inventory/InventoryPage.tsx)
- Disable the "Deactivate" action and "Price & Audit History" (which exposes cost history) from `ProductActionMenu` when user is not an owner.

#### [MODIFY] [CustomerProfile.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/features/khata/CustomerProfile.tsx)
- Hide/disable the "Log Repayment" drawer button if the logged-in user is not the owner.

#### [MODIFY] [BillingPage.tsx](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/features/billing/BillingPage.tsx)
- In the bill history list drawer, hide or disable the "Cancel Bill" action for staff.
- Limit date filtering to the last 7 days by restricting date pickers or ignoring older selections for staff users.

